					&lt;p&gt;I don't remember much of the advantages of using beer in your hair, but it was &lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bNSCPod_Khk" rel="nofollow"&gt;popular in the 70s&lt;/a&gt;.  Variations across beer styles are much greater than variations across brands within a style, so if you know what style of beer you want to use, it should not matter much which brand you pick.  My recommendation is to go with the cheapest brand you can find within the style you want to use.&lt;/p&gt;

