					&lt;p&gt;I'm no expert but i'll give it a shot:&lt;/p&gt;

					&lt;p&gt;Jägermeister and other herbal liqueurs do contain herbal essences that probably have some effect on your body. But not in any medicinal quality, otherwise it couldn't be sold as food in the EU by law. There are strict rules (e.g. &lt;a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Directive_2001/83/EC" rel="nofollow"&gt;Directive 2001/83/EC&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;

					&lt;p&gt;In general the usefulness of digestifs for the digestion is heavily discussed (there are opinions that the alcohol takes away any positive effect the herbs might have). But i don't have any reliable sources at hand.&lt;/p&gt;

